				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">This article is about the group of Northern and Southwestern Chinese dialects.  For the official spoken standardized Chinese language (Putonghua/Guoyu), see <a href="Standard_Chinese" title="Standard Chinese">Standard Chinese</a>.</div>
<table class="infobox" cellspacing="3" style="border-spacing: 3px; width:22em;">
