<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Guanhua.png" class="image"><img alt="Guanhua.png" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/be/Guanhua.png/150px-Guanhua.png" width="150" height="135" class="thumbborder" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/be/Guanhua.png/225px-Guanhua.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/be/Guanhua.png/300px-Guanhua.png 2x" /></a><br />
<span style="">Guānhuà (<i>Mandarin</i>)<br />
